00:57:35,687 --> 00:57:38,787
<font color="yellow">They started it first. You saw it, too.</font>

868
00:57:38,847 --> 00:57:40,347
<font color="yellow">But still.</font>

869
00:57:40,947 --> 00:57:44,987
<font color="yellow">Don't you know whoever swings first is at a disadvantage?</font>

870
00:57:44,987 --> 00:57:47,017
<font color="yellow">They keep bullying me.</font>

871
00:57:47,017 --> 00:57:50,517
<font color="yellow">Why do you let them get into your head?</font>

872
00:57:50,717 --> 00:57:54,387
<font color="yellow">I can't help but to swing first when I'm angry.</font>

873
00:57:56,547 --> 00:57:58,347
<font color="yellow">- I'm sorry. - No, you shouldn't be.</font>

874
00:57:59,987 --> 00:58:01,347
<font color="yellow">This isn't on you.</font>

875
00:58:01,717 --> 00:58:03,647
<font color="yellow">This is all because of...</font>

876
00:58:03,947 --> 00:58:05,947
<font color="yellow">lack of the humanities.</font>

