00:58:06,387 --> 00:58:08,617
<font color="yellow">Excuse me? Lack of what?</font>

878
00:58:08,787 --> 00:58:10,117
<font color="yellow">The humanities.</font>

879
00:58:11,047 --> 00:58:12,717
<font color="yellow">The difference between people and animals...</font>

880
00:58:12,887 --> 00:58:15,517
<font color="yellow">is that people can think deeply...</font>

881
00:58:15,547 --> 00:58:17,117
