882
00:58:17,487 --> 00:58:19,947
<font color="yellow">In 1995, after there was a wave...</font>

883
00:58:20,047 --> 00:58:22,247
<font color="yellow">of the humanities in the States,</font>

884
00:58:22,487 --> 00:58:24,017
