00:59:06,687 --> 00:59:07,917
<font color="yellow">Seriously?</font>

899
00:59:08,847 --> 00:59:12,417
<font color="yellow">Seong Sik really said those things?</font>

900
00:59:12,747 --> 00:59:15,787
<font color="yellow">Yes, he did. It broke my heart.</font>

901
00:59:15,887 --> 00:59:17,147
<font color="yellow">Where is Hyung Seop?</font>

902
00:59:17,747 --> 00:59:20,387
<font color="yellow">He must have felt disappointed. He went for a hike.</font>

903
00:59:20,447 --> 00:59:22,817
<font color="yellow">Of course, he must have. That's enough to disappoint him.</font>

904
00:59:22,817 --> 00:59:24,947
<font color="yellow">You know how he raised them.</font>

905
00:59:25,047 --> 00:59:27,187
<font color="yellow">With his salary, he raised four children.</font>

906
00:59:27,187 --> 00:59:30,117
<font color="yellow">He sent them to colleges and married them off.</font>

907
00:59:30,187 --> 00:59:33,847
<font color="yellow">He did his best raising them. How can he say those ungrateful things?</font>

908
00:59:33,947 --> 00:59:36,487
<font color="yellow">My goodness. I'm going to talk to him. Is he home?</font>

