00:59:36,617 --> 00:59:37,717
<font color="yellow">No.</font>

910
00:59:38,347 --> 00:59:40,187
<font color="yellow">He went out early in the morning.</font>

911
00:59:40,447 --> 00:59:43,647
<font color="yellow">Lock the door so he can't come in.</font>

912
00:59:43,647 --> 00:59:46,617
<font color="yellow">Do you think he can't come in because I lock the door?</font>

913
00:59:47,047 --> 00:59:50,187
<font color="yellow">This is why we shouldn't have been nice to our children.</font>

914
00:59:51,017 --> 00:59:55,047
<font color="yellow">This is how he treats us. We raised, clothed, fed, and educated him.</font>

915
00:59:55,847 --> 00:59:59,087
<font color="yellow">We even let him stay on the first floor. I don't even know...</font>

916
00:59:59,087 --> 01:00:00,887
<font color="yellow">what else he wants that desperately to talk to us like that.</font>

917
01:00:06,547 --> 01:00:08,447
<font color="yellow">Are you crying because of that?</font>

918
01:00:09,147 --> 01:00:11,117
<font color="yellow">This is breaking my heart, Mother.</font>

919
01:00:11,317 --> 01:00:12,947
<font color="yellow">What a punk.</font>

920
01:00:13,517 --> 01:00:15,887
<font color="yellow">When he comes home, I'm going to kill him.</font>

921
01:00:19,687 --> 01:00:22,187
<font color="yellow">To be honest, your script is good.</font>

922
01:00:22,687 --> 01:00:25,347
<font color="yellow">It's tightly constructed and the characters are vivid.</font>

923
01:00:25,547 --> 01:00:26,787
<font color="yellow">I feel as if the characters are real.</font>

924
01:00:27,947 --> 01:00:29,047
<font color="yellow">However,</font>

925
01:00:29,647 --> 01:00:33,247
<font color="yellow">do you think they need to go home before midnight like Cinderella?</font>

926
01:00:34,317 --> 01:00:35,947
<font color="yellow">What do you mean by that?</font>

927
01:00:35,987 --> 01:00:39,447
<font color="yellow">I'm telling you to let loose. Don't restrict yourself.</font>

928
01:00:41,247 --> 01:00:43,717
<font color="yellow">When I look at your script, I can see you in it.</font>

929
01:00:45,147 --> 01:00:47,517
<font color="yellow">Why aren't you confident about love?</font>

930
01:00:47,517 --> 01:00:49,917
<font color="yellow">You told me you can love confidently in your writing.</font>

931
01:00:53,287 --> 01:00:54,317
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

932
01:00:55,987 --> 01:00:58,417
<font color="yellow">Like I told you before, you have to change the title.</font>

933
01:00:58,887 --> 01:01:01,047
<font color="yellow">As you revise your script little by little,</font>

934
01:01:01,287 --> 01:01:03,347
<font color="yellow">you will think of a title you like.</font>

935
01:01:04,447 --> 01:01:05,587
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

936
01:01:07,817 --> 01:01:09,887
<font color="yellow">By the way, there is...</font>

937
01:01:10,117 --> 01:01:12,517
<font color="yellow">a book in my room that would be helpful for you.</font>

938
01:01:40,547 --> 01:01:41,887
<font color="yellow">Who can it be at this hour?</font>

939
01:01:42,517 --> 01:01:44,147
<font color="yellow">I'm not sure. Who is it?</font>

940
01:01:48,817 --> 01:01:52,087
<font color="yellow">Oh, my. Who are you?</font>

941
01:01:52,187 --> 01:01:54,947
<font color="yellow">Hello. My name is Bang Mi Joo.</font>

942
01:01:55,347 --> 01:01:57,117
<font color="yellow">Look who it is.</font>

943
01:01:57,247 --> 01:02:00,247
<font color="yellow">You're Seong Joon's girlfriend who was here the last time.</font>

944
01:02:00,787 --> 01:02:03,117
<font color="yellow">- What? - Yes. How have you been?</font>

945
01:02:03,117 --> 01:02:05,847
<font color="yellow">I've been great. Please come in.</font>

946
01:02:06,087 --> 01:02:08,147
<font color="yellow">You said you'd visit again, and you really did.</font>

947
01:02:09,617 --> 01:02:12,947
<font color="yellow">Say hello. She's Seong Joon's mom.</font>

948
01:02:13,517 --> 01:02:16,417
<font color="yellow">- Oh, I see. Hello. - Hi.</font>

949
01:02:16,617 --> 01:02:18,487
<font color="yellow">- Welcome. - These are for you.</font>

950
01:02:18,687 --> 01:02:20,517
<font color="yellow">Gosh. Thank you.</font>

951
01:02:20,717 --> 01:02:23,387
<font color="yellow">- Okay. - Jeong Ae. Where is Seong Joon?</font>

952
01:02:23,447 --> 01:02:27,447
<font color="yellow">He went to the rooftop to do something with Dong Hui.</font>

953
01:02:27,517 --> 01:02:31,147
<font color="yellow">You should go and tell him to hurry downstairs. His girlfriend is here.</font>

954
01:02:31,287 --> 01:02:33,247
<font color="yellow">What is he doing with Dong Hui?</font>

955
01:02:33,347 --> 01:02:34,847
<font color="yellow">Please come inside.</font>

956
01:02:35,817 --> 01:02:37,987
<font color="yellow">- Okay. - Goodness.</font>

957
01:02:38,487 --> 01:02:39,817
<font color="yellow">Please have a seat here.</font>

958
01:02:42,047 --> 01:02:44,447
<font color="yellow">- Did you say your name was Mi Joo? - Yes.</font>

959
01:02:44,547 --> 01:02:46,387
<font color="yellow">Gosh, you're so pretty.</font>

960
01:02:46,987 --> 01:02:48,217
<font color="yellow">Thank you.</font>

961
01:02:48,817 --> 01:02:51,287
<font color="yellow">What are you doing? Call Seong Joon.</font>

962
01:02:51,917 --> 01:02:52,917
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

963
01:02:55,917 --> 01:02:57,417
<font color="yellow">Mom. We're here.</font>

964
01:03:06,017 --> 01:03:07,887
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon. Hi.</font>

965
01:03:08,347 --> 01:03:10,087
<font color="yellow">You're here.</font>

966
01:03:10,387 --> 01:03:14,587
<font color="yellow">What were you doing with Dong Hui? Didn't you know she was coming?</font>

967
01:03:14,847 --> 01:03:18,687
<font color="yellow">No. I just wanted to meet Seong Joon's parents so badly.</font>

968
01:03:18,747 --> 01:03:21,587
<font color="yellow">I just came here to give you new year's greeting. He didn't know.</font>

969
01:03:22,587 --> 01:03:24,187
<font color="yellow">Hello, Dong Hui.</font>

970
01:03:26,447 --> 01:03:27,447
<font color="yellow">Hello.</font>

971
01:03:27,617 --> 01:03:29,917
<font color="yellow">Do you and Dong Hui know each other?</font>

972
01:03:30,187 --> 01:03:32,617
<font color="yellow">Of course. She works at our company.</font>

973
01:03:34,187 --> 01:03:35,487
<font color="yellow">Oh, my. Really?</font>

974
01:03:36,217 --> 01:03:40,187
<font color="yellow">Well... I should go upstairs now. Goodbye.</font>

975
01:03:59,187 --> 01:04:01,047
<font color="yellow">Gosh. You're a director?</font>

976
01:04:01,517 --> 01:04:03,947
<font color="yellow">Yes. That's right.</font>

977
01:04:04,317 --> 01:04:05,887
<font color="yellow">Her father is the chairman.</font>

978
01:04:06,647 --> 01:04:08,917
<font color="yellow">- Goodness, Seong Joon. - Mom.</font>

979
01:04:09,147 --> 01:04:12,947
<font color="yellow">But Seong Joon has helped me a lot since I was a new employee,</font>

980
01:04:13,017 --> 01:04:15,287
<font color="yellow">so I listen to everything he says.</font>

981
01:04:15,947 --> 01:04:17,587
<font color="yellow">- Mi Joo. - Charming men...</font>

982
01:04:17,847 --> 01:04:21,117
<font color="yellow">are those who have a firm hand.</font>

983
01:04:21,947 --> 01:04:23,817
<font color="yellow">Do you have any siblings?</font>

984
01:04:24,147 --> 01:04:27,517
