985
01:04:27,787 --> 01:04:29,617
<font color="yellow">so I was jealous when I heard...</font>

986
01:04:29,847 --> 01:04:32,447
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon had two brothers and cousins.</font>

987
01:04:33,487 --> 01:04:36,887
<font color="yellow">I see. How long have you been seeing each other?</font>

988
01:04:37,117 --> 01:04:39,747
<font color="yellow">We've known each other for five years,</font>

989
01:04:39,917 --> 01:04:42,617
<font color="yellow">and we've been dating for three years.</font>

990
01:04:43,817 --> 01:04:46,487
<font color="yellow">- You should get married now, then. - Grandma.</font>

991
01:04:46,987 --> 01:04:48,847
<font color="yellow">My father is also...</font>

992
01:04:48,917 --> 01:04:51,787
<font color="yellow">watching Seong Joon carefully as his successor.</font>

993
01:04:52,117 --> 01:04:53,347
<font color="yellow">Oh, my.</font>

994
01:04:54,087 --> 01:04:56,617
<font color="yellow">You still can't take away my dear Seong Joon.</font>

995
01:04:56,887 --> 01:05:00,017
<font color="yellow">Of course. I'll move out of my house myself.</font>

996
01:05:00,947 --> 01:05:03,747
<font color="yellow">No need to discuss. You should get married now. It'd be perfect.</font>

997
01:05:04,187 --> 01:05:08,147
<font color="yellow">Since his brothers got married, there haven't been any weddings.</font>

998
01:05:08,947 --> 01:05:11,087
<font color="yellow">Now it's time to have one.</font>

999
01:05:11,287 --> 01:05:14,217
<font color="yellow">Jeong Ae. How long has it been since we had a new family member?</font>

1000
01:05:14,247 --> 01:05:17,787
<font color="yellow">It's been 16 years because Chang Soo and Ji Hoon are 15.</font>

1001
01:05:18,247 --> 01:05:20,917
<font color="yellow">But Mother. I just met her.</font>

1002
01:05:20,987 --> 01:05:23,187
<font color="yellow">Talking about their wedding must be uncomfortable for her, too.</font>

1003
01:05:23,187 --> 01:05:25,447
<font color="yellow">No, it's not. I met my husband...</font>

1004
01:05:25,517 --> 01:05:28,847
<font color="yellow">for the first time at the wedding, but we had a wonderful marriage.</font>

1005
01:05:30,287 --> 01:05:31,747
<font color="yellow">Really? Oh, my.</font>

1006
01:05:33,287 --> 01:05:35,587
<font color="yellow">Grandma, Mom. She should go now.</font>

1007
01:05:35,787 --> 01:05:37,287
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry she visited so abruptly.</font>

1008
01:05:38,147 --> 01:05:40,047
<font color="yellow">- Why should she go? - I'm sorry.</font>

1009
01:05:40,417 --> 01:05:42,287
<font color="yellow">Come on, Mi Joo. You should go.</font>

1010
01:05:47,017 --> 01:05:49,217
<font color="yellow">I actually have things to do.</font>

1011
01:05:49,347 --> 01:05:51,047
<font color="yellow">I'll visit you again next time.</font>

1012
01:05:51,217 --> 01:05:52,987
<font color="yellow">Sure. I'll see you next time.</font>

1013
01:05:53,187 --> 01:05:55,847
<font color="yellow">Let's have dinner together, then.</font>

1014
01:05:56,117 --> 01:05:59,987
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon's dad isn't home right now.</font>

1015
01:05:59,987 --> 01:06:01,647
<font color="yellow">The rest of the family isn't, either.</font>

1016
01:06:01,917 --> 01:06:05,087
<font color="yellow">Okay, Grandmother. I'll see you next time, Mother.</font>

1017
01:06:05,247 --> 01:06:06,717
<font color="yellow">All right. Goodbye.</font>

1018
01:06:06,747 --> 01:06:08,787
<font color="yellow">I'm disappointed that you're leaving so soon.</font>

1019
01:06:09,687 --> 01:06:11,287
<font color="yellow">I'll see her off.</font>

1020
01:06:11,817 --> 01:06:12,817
<font color="yellow">Okay.</font>

1021
01:06:20,687 --> 01:06:21,917
<font color="yellow">Gosh.</font>

1022
01:06:26,887 --> 01:06:29,487
<font color="yellow">- What are you doing? - I'm going to go now.</font>

1023
01:06:35,887 --> 01:06:36,917
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon.</font>

1024
01:06:43,517 --> 01:06:46,417
<font color="yellow">I'm sorry. Please cut me some slack.</font>

1025
01:06:47,147 --> 01:06:49,487
<font color="yellow">What am I supposed to do? I just like you so much.</font>

1026
01:06:50,087 --> 01:06:51,617
<font color="yellow">That's why I went to your house.</font>

1027
01:06:51,817 --> 01:06:55,187
<font color="yellow">I know it's mean and humiliating, but I went anyway.</font>

1028
01:07:10,887 --> 01:07:12,087
<font color="yellow">I told you before.</font>

1029
01:07:13,287 --> 01:07:14,547
<font color="yellow">I don't love you.</font>

1030
01:07:14,847 --> 01:07:16,917
<font color="yellow">You're wrong. You can love me.</font>

1031
01:07:17,917 --> 01:07:19,887
<font color="yellow">You'll just have to try.</font>

1032
01:07:20,387 --> 01:07:21,387
<font color="yellow">Mi Joo.</font>

1033
01:07:21,487 --> 01:07:24,217
<font color="yellow">I can't give you up. Never.</font>

1034
01:07:25,947 --> 01:07:27,387
<font color="yellow">Seong Joon.</font>

1035
01:07:28,547 --> 01:07:29,747
<font color="yellow">Do you think...</font>

1036
01:07:31,387 --> 01:07:32,817
<font color="yellow">you can try to love someone?</font>

1037
01:07:34,817 --> 01:07:36,987
<font color="yellow">During those five years that we've spent together,</font>

1038
01:07:38,187 --> 01:07:39,647
<font color="yellow">I found you beautiful,</font>

1039
01:07:40,287 --> 01:07:41,987
<font color="yellow">and reliable at times.</font>

1040
01:07:43,017 --> 01:07:45,117
<font color="yellow">Sometimes I felt comfortable around you like we're friends.</font>

1041
01:07:46,847 --> 01:07:48,417
<font color="yellow">But while we were seeing each other,</font>

1042
01:07:49,647 --> 01:07:51,747
<font color="yellow">I always felt a burden on my heart.</font>

1043
01:07:52,887 --> 01:07:54,917
<font color="yellow">It felt uncomfortable like you aren't really mine.</font>

1044
01:07:57,417 --> 01:07:58,747
<font color="yellow">It confused me.</font>

